graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Component"
        Frontend[React Frontend<br/>PatternFly UI]
        Backend[Fastify Backend<br/>Node.js API Server]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>OpenShift Auth]

        Frontend -->|serves| Backend
        OAuthProxy -->|protects| Frontend
        OAuthProxy -->|proxies auth| Backend
    end

    User[Data Scientist/User] -->|HTTPS/443| OAuthProxy

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        OdhApplication[OdhApplication CR<br/>Application Catalog]
        OdhDocument[OdhDocument CR<br/>Documentation/Tutorials]
        OdhDashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig CR<br/>Feature Flags & Config]
        AcceleratorProfile[AcceleratorProfile CR<br/>GPU/Accelerator Profiles]
        OdhQuickStart[OdhQuickStart CR<br/>Guided Tutorials]
    end

    Backend -->|creates/reads| OdhApplication
    Backend -->|reads| OdhDocument
    Backend -->|manages| OdhDashboardConfig
    Backend -->|manages| AcceleratorProfile
    Backend -->|reads| OdhQuickStart

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>Resource Management]
        OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Authentication]
        Thanos[Thanos Querier<br/>Metrics]
    end

    Backend -->|HTTPS/443| K8sAPI
    OAuthProxy -->|HTTPS/443| OAuthServer
    Backend -->|HTTPS/9092| Thanos

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        ODHOperator[ODH Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster]
        Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CRD]
        KServe[KServe<br/>ServingRuntime]
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Model Deployment]
        Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>ML Workflows]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Model Versioning]
    end

    Backend -->|reads status| ODHOperator
    Backend -->|creates/manages| Notebooks
    Backend -->|manages| KServe
    Backend -->|manages| ModelMesh
    Backend -->|integrates| Pipelines
    Backend -->|manages| ModelRegistry

    subgraph "OpenShift Integration"
        ConsoleLink[ConsoleLink<br/>Application Menu]
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>External Access]
    end

    OAuthProxy -.->|registered in| ConsoleLink
    Route -->|routes to| OAuthProxy

    style Frontend fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Backend fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OdhApplication fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style OdhDocument fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style OdhDashboardConfig fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style AcceleratorProfile fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style OdhQuickStart fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OAuthServer fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Thanos fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Notebooks fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
